Puppet module: augeas

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages augeas software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include augeas              # Install and run augeas with standard configurations.
include augeas::disable     # Disable augeas service.
include augeas::disableboot # Disable augeas service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include augeas::absent      # Remove augeas package.

DEPENDENCIES:
